{"lemma":"لُقاطِ","slug":"لُقاطِ","root":"ل.ق.ط","root_slug":"ل-ق-ط","root_link":"/words/roots/ل-ق-ط","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n37920","n37921","n37922","n37926"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%84%D9%8F%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%B7%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n37920","headword_ar":"لَقَاطٌ","root":"lqT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laqaTN","text_ar":"لَقَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the latter part of the paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n37921","headword_ar":"لُقَاطٌ","root":"lqT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laqaTN","text_ar":"لَقَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n37922","headword_ar":"لِقَاطٌ","root":"lqT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 3. ―         -b2-  [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"act of picking up the ears of corn which the reaping-hooks miss;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"act denoted in the explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laqaATN","text_ar":"لَقَاطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (JK, K, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa yataEay~a$u biAlil~qaATi Eani All~aqaATi","text_ar":"هُوَ يَتَعَيَّشُ بِالِلّقَاطِ عَنِ اللَّقَاطِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He constrains himself to obtain the means of life,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he obtains what is barely sufficient for his sustenance, by picking up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gleaning, from the ears of corn which the reaping-hooks have missed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TK: but there given without any syll. signs.) [If the reading intended be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAll~aqaATi Eani All~iqaATi","text_ar":"بِاللَّقَاطِ عَنِ اللِّقَاطِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the meaning of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liqaATN","text_ar":"لِقَاطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"act of missing ears of corn with the reapinghook;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as is implied in the K, where"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laqaATN","text_ar":"لَقَاطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is imperfectly explained: but this I think improbable.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laqaATN","text_ar":"لَقَاطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liqaATN","text_ar":"لِقَاطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"are [respectively] like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSaAdN","text_ar":"حَصَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as signifying what is “ reaped ”] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiSaAdN","text_ar":"حِصَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as signifying the act of “ reaping ”]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n37926","headword_ar":"لَقَّاطٌ","root":"lqT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laAqiTN","text_ar":"لَاقِطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}